Former Chairman and chairmanship nominee of Independent National Electoral Commission, Prof Mahmood Yakubu, has urged the Nigerian Senate to pass the amended Electoral Act for assent by the President. Yakubu made the call when he appeared before the Senate for the confirmation of his nomination for the second and final term as INEC Chairman. Mahmood Yakubu See Also






